name: Wittin's Sandcrawler
Lore: 'Patrols the Dune Sea searching for lost droids and other items worth scavenging. Armor reinforced to protect against krayt dragon attacks. Enclosed.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. May add 1 driver and 7 passengers. While your Jawa is aboard, this vehicle and your Jawas at same site are immune to attrition < 3. Power +2 if Wittin at same site.',
